  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个支持多语言附件的完整流程。核心需求是让用户能够为不同locale上传不同的hero_image文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ModelCanonical",
        "View",
        "UserBrowser"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以不是简单的文件替换，而是每个locale对应独立的attachment记录？需要Mobility来管理这个翻译层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Mobility",
        "ModelCanonical"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，我们要基于Mobility框架，但需要一个自定义的backend。现有的key-value或者table backend都不适合处理ActiveStorage的关联关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "Mobility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我从数据库层开始画。首先需要active_storage_attachments表，然后需要一个migration来添加locale字段并回填现有数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DB",
        "A",
        "M"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，migration是第一步。回填的时候要注意，现有记录默认用I18n.default_locale。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M",
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我画出了Database子图包含active_storage_attachments表，以及Migration节点指向它。接下来是Mobility的初始化部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DB",
        "A",
        "M"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要Mobility initializer。它要负责require我们自定义的backend，然后register到Mobility框架里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Init",
        "B",
        "Mobility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了：Initializer节点分出两条线，一条require backend指向Attachments backend，另一条register backend指向Mobility.register_backend。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Init",
        "B",
        "Mobility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "backend文件位置放在lib/mobility/backends下面，命名要符合Mobility的约定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "backend需要提供apply_to和setup方法吧？这是Mobility backend的标准接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "Apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。Apply节点代表AttachmentsBackend的apply_to和setup方法，它会定义模型上的关联和访问器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Apply",
        "Assoc",
        "Accessors"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
