      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我画出了B指向Apply，然后Apply分出两条线：一条定义associations（has_many hero_image_attachments_all和has_one hero_image_attachment），另一条定义accessors。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "Apply",
        "Assoc",
        "Accessors"
